node.accessibility_caption: Photo by New York Bucket List in The DL with @nybucketlist. May be an image of furniture and text that says 'BUCKET LISTERS A Tropical Rooftop Party is Coming to LES Labor Day Weekend'.

node.text: Tag your party crew! 🥂🌴🥳 Summer is still sizzling at The DL's tropical Rooftop Saturday series! Starting Saturday of Labor Day Weekend come hang with local djs, cheers with your crew, and take in this tropical paradise! Exclusive tickets are available for a limited time at Bucketlisters.com or link-in-bio @NYBucketlist 🎟
